   | Regression | X/5 |
   | Design | X/5 |
   | **Average** | **X.X/5** |

   ## Review Findings
   - High confidence: N findings
   - Auto-fixed: M findings
   - Models used: Claude structured ✓ Claude adversarial ✓/✗ {{ adversarial_model }} ✓/✗

